com.facebook
Interface GraphPlace

All Superinterfaces:
GraphObject
public interface GraphPlace
extends GraphObject

Provides a strongly-typed representation of a Place as defined by the Graph API. Note that this interface is intended to be used with GraphObjectWrapper and not implemented directly.
